   <a href="https://rapidautoshipping.com/services/enclosed-shipping" target="_blank"><strong>Enclosed car transport</strong></a> is distinct from open carriers in that the vehicles are transported in a closed trailer, protecting them from weather and the surrounding environment. Enclosed storage is a popular choice for owners of classic, rare, expensive, custom, luxury, and antique vehicles.
